 working.”</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-texas-chainsaw-massacre"><em>The Texas Chainsaw Massacre</em></a> team <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/gun-interactive">Gun Interactive</a> assured players that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-texas-chain-saw-massacre-dev-talks-about-the-friday-the-13th-elephant-in-the-room-3483623">the game would not encounter the same stumbling blocks</a> as <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/friday-the-13th-the-game"><em>Friday The 13th: The Game</em></a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xboxs-new-anti-toxicity-system-grants-players-eight-chances-to-change-their-behaviour-3483744">Xbox&#39;s new anti-toxicity system grants players up to eight chances to change their behaviour</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
